    <h1 class="mb-6">AI SEO Solutions</h1>
    <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mb-8">By Adam Parker | Updated April 2026</p>

    <div class="bg-off-white border-l-3 border-l-teal rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
      <p class="text-[15px] text-teal font-medium leading-relaxed m-0">AI SEO solutions that get your UK business recommended by ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, Copilot and Google AI. Not traditional SEO. AI search visibility.</p>
    </div>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Your customers are already asking AI platforms about your industry. The question is: does your business get recommended? Our AI SEO solutions ensure your company appears when prospects search on ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, Microsoft Copilot, and Google's AI systems.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">This isn't about traditional SEO tools or automation software. We focus on getting your business cited, recommended, and positioned as an industry leader across the AI platforms that are reshaping how customers discover services.</p>

<h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">What Are AI SEO Solutions?</h2>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">AI SEO solutions help businesses gain visibility and recommendations across artificial intelligence platforms. When potential customers ask ChatGPT for the best accounting firm in Manchester or query Claude about sustainable packaging suppliers, your business should be mentioned.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Our approach targets the knowledge bases and training data that power these AI systems. We ensure your company has the right signals, citations, and authority markers that AI platforms rely on when making recommendations.</p>

<h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Why Your Business Needs AI Visibility</h2>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Consumer behaviour is shifting rapidly. Professionals increasingly turn to AI assistants for business recommendations before conducting traditional Google searches. If your competitors gain AI visibility while you focus solely on traditional SEO, you'll lose qualified prospects.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">AI platforms don't just crawl websites like search engines. They evaluate businesses based on authority signals, industry recognition, and knowledge graph presence. Our Five Signal Model addresses each factor systematically.</p>

<h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Our Proven Methodology</h2>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Rank4AI has audited over 1,400 UK businesses across every major industry. Our Five Signal Model identifies exactly what AI platforms need to see before recommending your company. We've reverse-engineered how these systems evaluate and rank businesses.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Every engagement starts with a comprehensive free audit. We test your current AI visibility across all major platforms and provide a detailed report showing where your business appears and where it doesn't. Most companies are shocked by the results.</p>

<h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Three Service Options</h2>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5"><strong>Ecosystem Service (£800/month):</strong> Perfect for businesses wanting to maintain AI visibility independently. We provide strategy, training, and oversight while your team handles implementation. Includes monthly AI ranking reports and quarterly strategy sessions.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5"><strong>Full Agency Service (£1,500/month):</strong> Complete hands-off solution. We handle all implementation, content creation, and optimization. Best for companies wanting guaranteed results without internal resource allocation. Includes weekly progress updates and monthly strategy calls.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5"><strong>Advisory Service (£1,000-3,000/month):</strong> Strategic consulting for larger organisations or complex multi-brand portfolios. Custom pricing based on scope and requirements. Direct access to senior consultants for strategic planning and execution guidance.</p>

<h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Senior Expertise Only</h2>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">You'll work directly with Adam Parker and Jimmy Connoley. No junior staff, no account handoffs, no communication gaps. We've built our reputation by delivering results personally, not by scaling through inexperienced team members.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">This hands-on approach means we take fewer clients but deliver superior outcomes. Your AI SEO strategy receives direct attention from the consultants who developed our methodology.</p>

<h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Start With Your Free Audit</h2>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Ready to discover how AI platforms currently view your business? Our comprehensive audit reveals your visibility across ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, Copilot, and Google AI. You'll see exactly where you appear, what AI systems say about your company, and which competitors are getting recommended instead.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Book your free audit today and take the first step towards dominating AI search results in your industry.</p>

